    <h3>Fixed Bowl vs Removable Bowl Spiral Mixers</h3>
    <p>Most spiral mixers in the 5–50kg range have a fixed bowl — the bowl is part of the machine and stays in place. Larger industrial spiral mixers (50kg+) often have removable bowls on wheels, allowing you to roll the full bowl away after mixing and roll in the next batch immediately, minimising downtime between mixes. Removable bowl systems are significantly more expensive but increase throughput substantially in high-volume operations.</p>

